entries.journal_entry_description: Help Lt. Jasper find out what the rogue CorSec are plotting.
entries.journal_entry_title: Find out what the Rogue CorSec Are Doing
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Meet with Jonset, an informant trusted by Lt. Jasper, at the Coronet cantina. Find out what he knows about recent rogue CorSec activities.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find the secret meeting Jonset told you about that's being held by rogue CorSec and Ragtags.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Disperse the meeting by fighting Ragtags and rogue CorSec.
entries.task02_task_display_string_1: Defeat Rogue CorSec at the Meeting
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Access the rogue CorSec data terminal that was left behind as the meeting was broken up.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Access the Rogue CorSec Data Terminal
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: From the data terminal, you find orders from the Diktat himself, Daclif Gallamby, issued to the Ragtags instructing them to smuggle spice into the capitol building. There is also ample proof that the Ragtags and the rogue CorSec are working together on something, but not enough to reveal what that might be.
entries.task04_message_box_text: From the data terminal, you find orders from the Diktat himself, Daclif Gallamby, issued to the Ragtags instructing them to smuggle spice into the capitol building. There is also ample proof that the Ragtags and the rogue CorSec are working together on something, but not enough to reveal what that might be.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Return to Lt. Jasper and relate to him what you found on the data terminal.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Defeat at least 6 Ragtags at the meeting.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Defeat at least 6 rogue CorSec troopers at the meeting.
